    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SpellWheel 是一款冒险策略游戏。通过结合魔法轮上的符文来施展各种法术来进行战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170660/extras/5eef1b517d970ef5384cbc639f19e825.poster.avif?t=1769388528\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170660/extras/5eef1b517d970ef5384cbc639f19e825.webm?t=1769388528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170660/extras/5eef1b517d970ef5384cbc639f19e825.mp4?t=1769388528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个敌人都提出独特的挑战，而每个施放的法术都会激怒你的对手，所以谨慎选择你的行动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170660/extras/afbebc8359a8051b71db21a04bb5b9c7.poster.avif?t=1769388528\" width=500 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170660/extras/afbebc8359a8051b71db21a04bb5b9c7.webm?t=1769388528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170660/extras/afbebc8359a8051b71db21a04bb5b9c7.mp4?t=1769388528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在旅程中，您将积累多种魔法。创意十足的玩家可以将强大的法术组合串联起来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170660/extras/19f03cd6e22321969446a5a46d6cdb6e.poster.avif?t=1769388528\" width=600 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170660/extras/19f03cd6e22321969446a5a46d6cdb6e.webm?t=1769388528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170660/extras/19f03cd6e22321969446a5a46d6cdb6e.mp4?t=1769388528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这一切都是为了拯救​​你心爱的人从死亡之地。但你走得越远，你就越会招来死神的注意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170660/extras/8dcc7f123f2792916ff57ec44032f430.avif?t=1769388528\" width=600 height=314 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于物理的滚轮界面</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回合制战斗和实时战斗的融合</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注重战略和精密计划的战斗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 个设计独特的手绘敌人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据你在战斗中的行为而产生多重结局的故事</p></li></ul>",
